## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **fezolinetant Veozah 2023** = first FDA NK3R antagonist menopause VMS. 60+ years HRT-only era 후 first non-hormonal targeted disease-modifying. SKYLIGHT-1+2+4 Phase 3. quantum-VQE 의 NK3R pocket fit.
2. **elinzanetant 2025 filing (Bayer)** = second NK1+NK3 dual antagonist. OASIS-1+2+3 Phase 3 + 2025 FDA filing. NK1 추가 = sleep 추가 효과 paradigm. dual receptor VQE 직접 fit.
3. **estetrol Estelle 2025 menopause** = second estrogen oral fetal-specific (placental E4). low-dose + 간 안전 + breast tissue 부드러움. 60+ year conjugated estrogens (Premarin) 후 next E.
4. **bazedoxifene + conjugated estrogen Duavee 2013** = SERM combo HRT — progestin 없이 endometrial protection. SERM pocket VQE leverage.
5. **ospemifene Osphena 2013 + prasterone Intrarosa 2016** = GSM + dyspareunia 임상 paradigm shift. SERM oral + DHEA intravaginal — non-estrogen alternative.
6. **paroxetine Brisdelle 2013 (low-dose)** = first non-hormonal FDA VMS pre-fezolinetant. 7.5 mg low-dose paroxetine — breast cancer survivor + HRT 금기 환자.
7. **WHI 2002 lessons** = combined estrogen + progestin (Prempro) 임상 시험 중단 — breast cancer + CHD + stroke + VTE 위험. HRT prescribing 80% drop. 2023+ fezolinetant 가 non-hormonal era 시작.
8. **vaginal estradiol cream + tablet + ring** = local GSM 임상 표준 — systemic exposure 최소. Vagifem + Estring + Premarin cream classical.
9. **gabapentin + clonidine + venlafaxine off-label VMS** = 60% VMS 환자 HRT 금기 — non-hormonal off-label era. fezolinetant 2023 + elinzanetant 2025 가 on-label era 전환.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, menopause 임상 의미 한정.

